Track it - Privacy Policy
Welcome to Track it! This Privacy Policy ("Policy") describes how ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and shares your personal information when you use the Track it mobile application ("App"). By using the App, you agree to the practices described in this Policy.
Share
1. Information We Collect
We collect the following types of personal information for the purposes described below:
Full Name:
We collect your full name which it is shared by you to enable the
                    functionality of the App.
2. Data Collection and Sharing with Third Parties
We use third-party analytics tools to collect and analyze data about how the App is used. This includes
                information such as app usage, device information, and crash reports. This data helps us improve the App's
                performance and user experience. The data collected is shared with third-party analytics providers for
                analysis.
In the event of app crashes or technical issues, we may collect diagnostic information, including crash logs
                and device information. This data is used for troubleshooting and improving the App's stability.
3. Data Security
We take data security seriously and have implemented measures to safeguard your personal information.
                However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is
                completely secure.
4. Updates to this Policy
We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time without prior notice. Any changes
                will be effective immediately upon posting the updated Policy on the App. Your continued use of the App
                after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised Policy.
